		<p id="answer-1" class="answer" style="display: none;">Figure Eight is perfect for gym climbers who are able to lead climb at least 5.9 indoors. Our average client has climbed for 1-2 years, and is looking to make one of their first serious outdoor trips. We make it easy to explore a new area by combining our expertise with excellent planning and trip logistics. Experienced climbers may choose to climb with Figure Eight for an introduction to an unfamiliar crag, or to take a luxurious climbing "vacation" with friends. Beginners are welcome on Figure Eight trips when accompanied by an experienced friend.</p>
