		<h4 id="question-4">What do I need to bring?</h4>
		<p id="answer-4" class="answer" style="display: none;">You'll need to supply your own harness, shoes, belay device, and headlamp. We'll remind you of the weather forecast for your trip, but please dress responsibly for hot afternoons or cold nights! Most locations have either swimming holes, hot springs, or hot tubs &mdash; so bring your swimsuit, too. Other optional items: beverages, board games, good music. Things you can leave at home: rope, deli meat, towels, bed linens, worries, Mountain Project printouts.</p>
	</div>
